{"tw": {"3377320": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Arcane Lust 18+", "steam_appid": 3377320, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "在 <strong>Arcane Lust 18+</strong> 中，進入一個充滿危險、熱情和波折的未來世界！這款視覺小說模擬遊戲挑戰您在一個機能失常的機器人狐族女孩的控制下生存 10 天，同時保持她的情感平衡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3d61e401507511d9870cecf5451a8287.poster.avif?t=1762448491\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3d61e401507511d9870cecf5451a8287.webm?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3d61e401507511d9870cecf5451a8287.mp4?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>在不久的將來，一個充滿超現實機械人的大型主題公園，讓遊客可以盡情發揮他們最狂野的幻想。Finn 是公園裡的機械師，他發現自己被困在以幻想為主題的區域 - 一片充滿神話生物的魔幻森林。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/bb0896181162cc87fe190482bd13742a.poster.avif?t=1762448491\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/bb0896181162cc87fe190482bd13742a.webm?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/bb0896181162cc87fe190482bd13742a.mp4?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>當 Finn 在一個廢棄的小木屋中醒來，發現 Aelin（一個安裝了機器人的狐狸女孩）離自己太近而感到不舒服時，一切就開始了。她已經斷開了與自己的聯繫，並認為 Finn 是她的 「命運」。更糟的是，她還在他身上戴上追蹤手鐲，將他綁在公園裡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/dc20ad90523eeaf773ef9c8cb0b12d33.poster.avif?t=1762448491\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/dc20ad90523eeaf773ef9c8cb0b12d33.webm?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/dc20ad90523eeaf773ef9c8cb0b12d33.mp4?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>在沒有後援的情況下（其他技術人員都忙著建造水下公園），Finn 必須在 Aelin 變幻莫測、渴求關注的行為下生存 10 天，同時還要處理自己不斷飆升的情緒。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/a19dd993a0008eb98c88e0039ed9dd39.poster.avif?t=1762448491\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/a19dd993a0008eb98c88e0039ed9dd39.webm?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/a19dd993a0008eb98c88e0039ed9dd39.mp4?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>🔑<strong>功能[/b］<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>情緒平衡系統 : 小心選擇你的行動，讓 Aelin 保持冷靜，避免她危險的發作。<br></li><li>探索公園 : 發現隱藏的地方、線索，並深入探索機器人的黑暗秘密。<br></li><li>成人內容： 辛辣的場景和熱情的時刻讓這趟旅程更加刺激。<br></li><li>糾纏不清的情節： 您的選擇會直接影響情節、您與 Aelin 的關係以及結局。<br></li><li>未來奇幻設定：尖端科技與魔法的獨特融合，讓樂園栩栩如生。<br><br>[Arcane Lust 18+[/b] 是一個關於生存、激情以及在現實與幻想碰撞的世界中發現真相的故事。您準備好迎接這場狂野的冒險了嗎？</li></ul></strong>", "about_the_game": "在 <strong>Arcane Lust 18+</strong> 中，進入一個充滿危險、熱情和波折的未來世界！這款視覺小說模擬遊戲挑戰您在一個機能失常的機器人狐族女孩的控制下生存 10 天，同時保持她的情感平衡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3d61e401507511d9870cecf5451a8287.poster.avif?t=1762448491\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3d61e401507511d9870cecf5451a8287.webm?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/webm; codec