s/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3d61e401507511d9870cecf5451a8287.poster.avif?t=1762448491\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3d61e401507511d9870cecf5451a8287.webm?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3d61e401507511d9870cecf5451a8287.mp4?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3a8c8498de2c15f8b531f5baacb150c8.avif?t=1762448491\" width=599 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the near future, a massive theme park filled with hyper-realistic androids lets visitors live out their wildest fantasies. Finn, a park mechanic, gets stuck in the middle of the fantasy-themed section — a magical forest full of mythical creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/a19dd993a0008eb98c88e0039ed9dd39.poster.avif?t=1762448491\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/a19dd993a0008eb98c88e0039ed9dd39.webm?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/a19dd993a0008eb98c88e0039ed9dd39.mp4?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It all kicks off when Finn wakes up in an abandoned cabin to find Aelin, a fox-girl android, getting way too close for comfort. She’s glitched out and now sees Finn as her “destiny.” Worse, she’s slapped a tracking bracelet on him, tying him to the park.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/dc20ad90523eeaf773ef9c8cb0b12d33.poster.avif?t=1762448491\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/dc20ad90523eeaf773ef9c8cb0b12d33.webm?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/dc20ad90523eeaf773ef9c8cb0b12d33.mp4?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With no backup available (the other techs are busy building an underwater park), Finn has to survive 10 days of Aelin’s unpredictable, attention-hungry behavior while managing her spiraling emotions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/da64e6bac6f938fb81c7f32fcd44f2bf.avif?t=1762448491\" width=598 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/bb0896181162cc87fe190482bd13742a.poster.avif?t=1762448491\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/bb0896181162cc87fe190482bd13742a.webm?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/bb0896181162cc87fe190482bd13742a.mp4?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/093b1762a1ccb0310a71466b98dab671.avif?t=1762448491\" width=600 height=104 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Emotional Balance System: Choose your actions carefully to keep Aelin calm and avoid her dangerous breakdowns.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the Park: Discover hidden locations, uncover clues, and dive into the dark secrets of the androids.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adult Content: Spicy scenes and steamy moments make this journey even more thrilling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Branching Storylines: Your choices directly shape the plot, your relationship with Aelin, and the ending.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Futuristic Fantasy Setting: A unique blend of cutting-edge tech and magical vibes brings the park to life.<br><br><strong>Arcane Lust 18+</strong> is about survival, passion, and uncovering the truth in a world where reality and fantasy collide. Are you ready for this wild ride?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/586ef90fee729f7954e527f6e76fad57.avif?t=1762448491\" width=598 height=180 /></span></p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/c94958a45eb6e9120aef8b4866586446.avif?t=1762448491\" width=598 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into a futuristic world of danger, passion, and crazy twists in <strong>Arcane Lust 18+</strong>! This visual novel-simulator challenges you to survive 10 intense days under the control of a malfunctioning fox-girl android while keeping her emotional balance in check.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3d61e401507511d9870cecf5451a8287.poster.avif?t=1762448491\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3d61e401507511d9870cecf5451a8287.webm?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3d61e401507511d9870cecf5451a8287.mp4?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/3a8c8498de2c15f8b531f5baacb150c8.avif?t=1762448491\" width=599 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the near future, a massive theme park filled with hyper-realistic androids lets visitors live out their wildest fantasies. Finn, a park mechanic, gets stuck in the middle of the fantasy-themed section — a magical forest full of mythical creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/a19dd993a0008eb98c88e0039ed9dd39.poster.avif?t=1762448491\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/a19dd993a0008eb98c88e0039ed9dd39.webm?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377320/extras/a19dd993a0008eb98c88e0039ed9dd39.mp4?t=1762448491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It all kicks off when Finn wakes up in an abandoned cabin to find Aelin, a fox-girl android, getting way too close for comfort. She’s glitched out and now sees Finn as her “destiny.” Worse, she’s slapped a tracking bracelet on him, tying him to the park.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://s